# ─── Configurazione personale (non committare nel repo pubblico) ──────────────
# .opencode/ is the legacy mirror dir (symlinked from .claude/). Most of its
# content is per-machine (personal skill mirror), but team-shared infrastructure
# lives alongside and should be tracked:
#   - settings.json: project-scoped hook config
#   - scripts/:      shared SessionStart/PostToolUse hooks
.opencode/*
!.opencode/settings.json
!.opencode/scripts/
